{"tid":960022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★None want！】iPad Pro變彎受 Apple前高層受不了狡辯：將它退貨！！","createTime":"2018-12-29T05:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T07:05:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a4c5ffb266af4f1892595c7381d77cbdc12cc634","tid":960022,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T05:32:55.000Z","msg":"不久之前有使用者反映新款iPad Pro容易變彎，不過蘋果高管認為這在可接受範圍內，並且不用太過於擔心。 不過有一位「特殊」的使用者可忍不了，他就是蘋果公司的<span style=\"color: red;\">前高級行銷總監邁克爾&middot;加滕伯格，他決定將機身變彎了的iPad Pro<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">退貨</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n在他的社交網站上，這位前蘋果公司員工認為iPad Pro出現的這種「彎曲」是不合理的，蘋果無法證實這是在設計公差範圍內的。<br />\n<br />\n雖然彎曲現在可能不是引起擔心的原因，但它最終<span style=\"color: red;\">可能會導致其它問題的出現，例如主機板上的接線鬆動</span>。 iPhone6和iPhone 6 Plus也出現了類似的問題，其「彎曲門」最終導致了觸控問題的出現。<br />\n<br />\n加滕伯格認為iPad Pro起售價並不便宜，蘋果沒有理由發售出廠就彎曲或日常使用時容易彎曲的平板電腦。 大多數人經常在旅行時將iPad放在包裡，在包裡會受到一定程度的壓力，如果容易出現彎曲的情況，那麼就會容易出現其它的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/402/993.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F402%2F993.htm&d=1RWWJ1soOO8DpV5GiEFapIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e2d59c9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/402/993.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9022154d4c3e8b5dc279b6cdcd07a984309d4121","tid":960022,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T05:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90780dc71cba6907392b1d423a41af52ef4bd613","tid":960022,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T05:33:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">變彎<del>受</del></span>"},{"pid":"54a45f84f7bf0cb954a06fa3b0206640e2d6948f","tid":960022,"uid":5178,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"reply